From: user
Date: Mon, 30 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] avcodec/hevc: add motion vector export support

Add ff_hevc_export_motion_vectors() which walks the per-PU motion
vector field (tab_mvf), merges adjacent prediction units that share
identical motion parameters into larger blocks, and attaches the
result as AV_FRAME_DATA_MOTION_VECTORS side data.

The export is gated on AV_CODEC_EXPORT_DATA_MVS (export_side_data)
and is invoked on the output path in ff_hevc_output_frames().

